quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,perfecit ego non covenant vos O Infans Adam ut vos non worship devil Ut he est tuus ardent enemy
  36,61,Ac ut vos worship Me alone Hoc est rectus path
  36,62,He misled multitudes de vos. Vos non possess any understanding
  36,63,Hoc est Hell promised vos
  36,64,Hodie vos burn it consequence tuus disbelief
  36,65,Feria nos sigillum their mouths their manus feet bear testis everything they perfecit
  36,66,Nos testimentum nos veil their eyes consequently when they seek path they non vide
  36,67,Nos testimentum nos freeze them in locus; ergo they potuit nec move forward nor iit
  36,68,"Whomever nos permit vivens pro ut long temporis, nos revert eum to marasmus! they non understand"
  36,69,quod nos taught eum (messenger) non est poetry nor est he (poet)! Hoc est formidable proof profound Quran
  36,70,To preach to those est alive expose disbelievers
  36,71,they non vide nos habuit created them noster suus manus livestock they suus
  36,72,Ac nos subdued them them; some they ride some they eat
  36,73,They derive alius benefits ex them alias prout drinks they non est appreciative
  36,74,They set DEUS alius deus perhaps they est de help to them
  36,75,On the contrary they non help them; they finis serving them prout devoted militis
  36,76,Ergo non saddened their utterances! Nos est fully aware de everything they conceal everything they declare
  36,77,human est non vide nos perfecit created eum ex tiny drop tunc he turns into ardent enemy
  36,78,He levabat question nos - dum forgetting his initial creation - Qui resurrect bones post they rotted
  36,79,Dictus Unus initiated them in the 1 locus resurrect them! He est fully aware de omnis creation
  36,80,He est Unus creates vos green trees fuel quae vos burn pro light
  36,81,Non est Unus created caelum terra able to recreate the same sic indeed; He est Creator Omniscient
  36,82,totus He perfecit carry any command est dictus to Est it est
  36,83,Ergo glory est 1 in whose manus est sovereignty totus things Eum vos returned
  37,1,arrangers columns
  37,2,blamers de those to blamed
  37,3,reciters messages
  37,4,Tuus deus est unus
  37,5,Dominus de caelum terra everything them Dominus de easts
  37,6,Nos adorned inferior caelum adorning planets
  37,7,Nos custos it omnis malus devil
  37,8,They non spy High Society; they get bombarded omnis side
  37,9,They condemned they incurred eternal retribution
  37,10,any de them ventures charge outer limits he struck fierce projectile
  37,11,Ask them Est they difficult create alius creations? Nos created them ex wet mud
  37,12,dum vos awed they mock
  37,13,When reminded they non take heed
  37,14,When they vide proof they ridicule it
  37,15,They dictus Hoc est obviously magic
  37,16,Post nos abiit become dust bones nos resurrected
  37,17,Et noster ancient patres
  37,18,Dictus Sic vos forcibly summoned
  37,19,Totus takes est 1 nudge whereupon they stand looking
  37,20,They dictus Woe nos; hoc est Feria Judgment
  37,21,Hoc est feria decision vos used disbelieve in